                    <h3>Prototypes, testing and iteration</h3>
                    <p>
                        Potential designs get tested in different ways depending on the project, but could include:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>paper prototypes</li>
                        <li>interactive wireframes with tools like framer, sketch or native code</li>
                        <li>A/B testing</li>
                        <li>usertesting.com or similar</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>After testing, if we haven’t seen the results we want, we iterate and test again, until we’ve got
                        something that’s mature, solid and can demonstrate that it’s solving our challenge.
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

</section>


